         <notesStmt>
            <note>Imperfect at the beginning. Folios missing after folio 304. Slightly water-damaged.  Last leaves slightly worm-eaten.</note>
            <note>The last six leaves belonged to a different manuscript. Contain midrashic expositions on parashah Ṿa-yelekh and Ha᾿azinu. 
								Mikha᾿el ben Mosheh: inscribed, folio 2r. 
								Raḥamim ben Shemu᾿el Malkiowner: inscribed, folio 369r. </note>
